      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The finalization of Basis of Allotment for <!-- -->Mahickra Chemicals IPO<!-- --> will be done on <!-- -->Monday, April 23, 2018<!-- -->, and the allotted shares will be credited to your demat account by <!-- -->Wednesday, April 25, 2018<!-- -->. Check the <a href=\"/ipo_allotment_status/mahickra-chemicals-ipo/854/\" title=\"Mahickra Chemicals IPO Allotment Status\">Mahickra Chemicals IPO<!-- --> allotment status</a>.</p></div>"
